213
00:13:40,870 --> 00:13:43,202
The other day he asked
about my retirement plan.

214
00:13:43,372 --> 00:13:46,773
Well, he cares about you, and he
wants you to be financially secure.

215
00:13:47,476 --> 00:13:50,445
You know Austin adores you.
I can see why.

216
00:13:50,846 --> 00:13:54,043
- Thank you, Bob.
- I might prefer Bobby after all.

217
00:13:54,216 --> 00:13:56,776
I mean, I like the...
I like the history.

218
00:14:04,994 --> 00:14:08,191
Two guys alone in the afternoon
watching <i>Doctor Zhivago</i>.

219
00:14:08,364 --> 00:14:11,595
- There's something gravely wrong here.
