225
00:14:25,447 --> 00:14:28,678
No. I want to go out. Come on,
I previewed some Internet ads for us.

226
00:14:28,851 --> 00:14:31,911
Internet ads? Come on,
I want Zhivago's Internet ad:

227
00:14:32,087 --> 00:14:35,648
"Tragic doctor/poet
