01:25:17,694 --> 01:25:21,186
Or better yet, go over there, break into
his house, throw yourself at him...

1361
01:25:21,364 --> 01:25:23,832
...make a complete fool of yourself.
It worked for me.

1362
01:25:24,100 --> 01:25:28,036
- It was very effective.
- No, he's with someone else.

1363
01:25:28,371 --> 01:25:31,738
I have to face it, it's just not
gonna work out with us.

1364
01:25:32,175 --> 01:25:34,575
And you'd really like it to,
wouldn't you?

1365
01:25:37,080 --> 01:25:39,275
