This is breaking my heart.

1366
01:25:39,449 --> 01:25:42,384
Mine too.
But let's look on the bright side.

1367
01:25:42,552 --> 01:25:44,179
- Your nails look fabulous.
- They do.

1368
01:25:44,487 --> 01:25:46,717
